t: Our Friend Rufus - Amazon Customer Service
s: For years, Rufus was a fixture at Amazon.com, dating back to the early days in the company's history. He belonged to Amazon's former editor-in-chief and principal engineer, and he accompanied them to the office every day. He's been affectionately called Amazon's shortest volunteer worker.
